{"tid":1196984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種先當差","createTime":"2019-06-10T01:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T01:07:41.000Z","uid":44954,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48fa6f3bc8ce5f63449e22422ae9fd5a6bc82b81","tid":1196984,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:03:53.000Z","msg":"唔好話乜打份工，揾飯啫。<br />\n根本就係助紂為虐。出糧俾你個個真係淋病咩？仲要又胡椒又盾咁對班乜柒都冇嘅市民。十鳩幾個圍個後生嘅。掉汽油彈個個都冇咁多人啦。<br />\n咁撚人上街，呢啲叫民意。我唔敢講每位賤種差佬係支持修例，但係每一個差佬都有份將香港逼到上末路。根本同雞都冇分別，一樣係為錢賣身。<br />\n最後呼籲一句，煩請block曬所有做緊或者企圖投考警察嘅「朋友」，一定要斷絕往來。因為道不同不相為謀。<br />\n最後如果12號要出嚟嘅，我地千其唔好放棄，唔好因為今日而氣餒，我知道大家都會有種無力感，但係有啲嘢唔趁而家做，將來一定會後悔。再講事情已經得到國際關注，只差一步咋，千其千其唔好放棄。香港係屬於我地，而唔係一班牛鬼蛇神。一定要守住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申00後，今年準備19歲。你地廿鳩幾歲個啲千其唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母淋奠越哦，食屎狗，含家剷</span>"},{"pid":"80e371fd9c3d5fff25473d7c5de1e06d5abc7afd","tid":1196984,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"唔衝又點會食椒食棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8257a82f35e158b7d74be64d69e212aa1be5f7b","tid":1196984,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共打手"},{"pid":"00a6615d1620ea62765d34d470b8f52a4146410c","tid":1196984,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80e371fd9c3d5fff25473d7c5de1e06d5abc7afd","tid":1196984,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:05:12.000Z","msg":"唔衝又點會食椒食棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"問題真係呢到？"}]}